snippet.title: Bot Land Trailer
snippet.description:
https://bot.land/ Make bots, automate their strategy, and crush other players without even having to be online!

Bot Land is still in Beta and won't be fully released until at least May, 2019. Despite that, the game is currently playable—find out more at https://bot.land/

The game is developed live on Twitch on most weekdays: https://twitch.tv/AdamLearnsLive Feel free to chat with Adam there directly and ask any questions you have about the game!
